---

<div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-12">
  <h3
    class="font-mono font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3"
  >
    Comentarios / Dudas
    <span
      class="text-xs font-sans font-medium text-[#ec4899] bg-[#ec4899]/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-[#ec4899]/20"
      >2</span
    >
  </h3>
  <div class="mb-12 relative group">
    <textarea
      class="w-full p-4 pl-4 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#ec4899]/20 focus:border-[#ec4899] focus:bg-white outline-none transition-all placeholder-gray-400 font-sans text-sm resize-none h-32"
      placeholder="Escribe tu duda o comentario..."></textarea>
    <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 flex items-center gap-2">
      <button
        class="bg-gray-900 hover:bg-black text-white text-xs font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded shadow-sm hover:shadow transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        Publicar Comentario
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="space-y-10">
    <div
      class="flex gap-4 md:gap-5 animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-2 duration-500"
    >
      <img
        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 object-cover border border-gray-100 shrink-0"
        src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCTGYjIxfECncQzlzXshw7vcNc5Y_E57nWlbVV7krwBaiw3Nw2wbr8YXZl7sqZ_bqUuep1qbkNdu67_YkZ_f7fhymFIUYTZ_xWHsD5733AzKxhZ67DapRt7_hKOGwQxXQStG9dDhh2nvkk7B5e2dYstJXk5YITUnJ3PI1ht-z4ypP_cTxZvyQ1zkaZB5V5PlXH6f8R5Sw9Vk0c0mwlrPeosb82QBcHjNqaqtHm23BKIw-mhGvQsdY6pQk4XQ7kiqYVD-PmS31c6Mq8"
      />
      <div class="flex-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
          <span class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm font-sans"
            >Ana García</span
          >
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">hace 2 horas</span>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white border border-gray-100 p-4 rounded-xl rounded-tl-none shadow-sm relative"
        >
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Excelente explicación sobre la inmutabilidad. ¿Recomiendas usar
            imágenes basadas en Alpine siempre para producción? He tenido
            algunos problemas con librerías nativas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <button
          class="text-gray-500 hover:text-[#ec4899] text-xs font-bold mt-2 ml-2 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 group"
        >
          <span
            class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px] group-hover:-rotate-12 transition-transform"
            >reply</span
          >
          Responder
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex gap-4 md:gap-5 animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-2 duration-700 delay-100"
    >
      <div
        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-linear-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs shrink-0 shadow-sm"
      >
        CR
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
          <span class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm font-sans"
            >Carlos R.</span
          >
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">hace 5 horas</span>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white border border-gray-100 p-4 rounded-xl rounded-tl-none shadow-sm relative"
        >
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Justo lo que necesitaba para mi pipeline de CI. ¡Gracias! La
            comparación con VMs dejó todo muy claro, especialmente el tema del
            aislamiento de procesos.
          </p>
        </div>
        <button
          class="text-gray-500 hover:text-[#ec4899] text-xs font-bold mt-2 ml-2 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 group"
        >
          <span
            class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px] group-hover:-rotate-12 transition-transform"
            >reply</span
          >
          Responder
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
